<H2><IMG SRC=images/maillist.gif ALT="" BORDER=0>
 What's this For Mother Earth mailinglist?
</H2>
Everybody who's intrested in our organisation 'For Mother Earth' is able 
to join this mailinglist.  When you complete the following form you 
receive our action reports, announcements, pressarticles, etc... by email.<P>

