<B><FONT SIZE=+1><P> <P>PRESS<BR>RELEASE<P><HR><p></font><FONT SIZE=-1>
<A HREF=/~fme/contact.html>Contact address:</a>
<P>Gewad 15<BR>9000 Gent, Belgium<BR>Phone +32-9-2334924<BR>Fax: +32-9-2337802<BR>
