 <H1>COUNTRY STATUS REPORTS</H1>
 <H2>OVERVIEW</H2>
</CENTER> 

<I><A HREF="laka.htm">Foundation LAKA</A> is a dutch documentation and 
 research centre on nuclear energy. During the <A HREF=../wae/waeidx.html>Walk across Europe</A> LAKA
 published on the countries the so-called Country Status Reports.
</I>
<P>

<H3>
