<DOCNO>WT25-B18-110</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA087-000626-B002-103</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~fme/wae/reports/wrep016.html 194.10.201.200 19970122081142 text/html 10557
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
