<HEAD><TITLE> Green Spring Party - Friday March 17 - Diogenes Nijmegen	</TITLE></HEAD>

<body>
<A HREF="/~fme/wae/waeidx.html"><IMG SRC="/~fme/images/walkhome.gif" ALT="Walk Across Europe Home Page"></A>

<H2>for immediate release</H2>
<H2>Green Spring Party - Friday March 17 - Diogenes Nijmegen  </H2>


<HR>
<H1>'Enjoy the Good Life. Pick the day, not the future' </H1>

Come to the Green Spring Party, March 17 in Diogenes, very near Nijmegen
CS. Enjoy eco-art, a magnificent concert of 'GREEN DREAM', and dance till
5 am on the best underground and house music. Great food and drinks,
organic quality. Entrence fee hfl 7,50; 2,50 discount with 10
milieukeurmerkjes. Sleeping accomodation and breakfast available. (Bring
sleeping bag). Take your friends along!<P>

The Walk across Europe for a Nuclear-free World will arrive in the
Netherlands on March 14, in Nijmegen on March 17. You can join the party
on Friday 17th, the Dodewaard action on Saturday 18th, or join the walk
for some days, weeks or months. Info: 080-223434 (Benno)<P>

The "Green Spring Party / Groene Lente Feest" is organized by Stichting
<A HREF="http://antenna.nl/~jma/jmp.html">Jongeren Milieu Producties</a> for vereniging <A HREF="http://antenna.nl/~jma/index.html">Jongeren
Milieu Aktief. </a>
Interested in becoming environmentally active at school, university, in
your town or wherever? Phone JMA: NL 030-316566 or email: <A HREF="mailto:jma@antenna.nl">jma@antenna.nl</a>.<P>

Your donation for our environmental work is more than welcome on Postbank
account 6240371.

