	<DD><A HREF="http://www.cwi.nl/cwi/people/Jack.Jansen/spunk/cookbook.html">Anarchist Cookbook</A>
	<DD>The <A HREF="http://www.geocities.com/WestHollywood/2163/bolintro.html">
	Bolsheviks and Workers Control</A> is a remarkable pamphlet by <I>Maurice Brinton</I>, 
	exposing the struggle that took place over the running of workplaces in the
	immediate aftermath of the Russian Revolution.
	<DD><A HREF="bookchin.html">Murray Bookchin: Social Anarchism or Lifestyle Anarchism</A>
	<DD><A HREF="makhno01.html">A poem by Nestor Makhno</A>
