<H3>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="atwork.gif" WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="40" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
!! Werken / Travaux / Under construction !!
<IMG SRC="atwork.gif" WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="40" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
</CENTER>
</H3>

<H1>
<CENTER>
	John CAGE
</CENTER>
</H1>

<HR>

<P>
<CENTER>
"... a composer is simply someone who tells other people what to do.<BR>
I find this an unattractive way of getting things done.<BR>
I'd like our activities to be more social and anarchically so."
<P>
<I>John Cage, A Year From Monday (New Lectures and Writings),
<BR>Middletown, Wesleyan Univ. Press, 1967, p. ix-x</I>
<P>
