<DOCOLDNO>IA087-000625-B028-83</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~owwbel/equita.html 194.10.201.200 19970122034205 text/html 3964
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
