<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~owwbel/cruncho.html 194.10.201.200 19970122034250 text/html 2831
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 04:43:08 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
