<DOCNO>WT25-B18-231</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA087-000625-B031-356</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~owwbel/crita.html 194.10.201.200 19970122035949 text/html 3055
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
