<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~owwbel/coracari.html 194.10.201.200 19970122104922 text/html 3536
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 11:49:38 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
Content-Length: 3330
Last-Modified: Tuesday, 16-Apr-96 13:24:43 GMT
