<center><h1>@De Nar@</h1></center>
<center><img src="write.gif" alt=""></center>
<hr noshade width=23%>
<p><h3>Hello,</h3>
<p><font size="4"><b>W</b></font>elcome at the homepage of 'De Nar'. 
You've just arrived on the only page on this site that isn't written in 
Dutch. Because of the already large amount of anarchist sites on the Net, 
we decided to make up this homepage in Dutch, 
instead of in English. 
<p><font size=4><b>'D</b></font>e Nar' is a Belgian Anarchist Magazine 
concerned with the small community of anarchists in our country. We put 
out a monthly magazine, make up this homepage an distribute leaflets, 
stickers, brochures, etc. 
<p><font size=4><b>A</b></font>nd of course, we most humbly
apologize for the bad English, the spelling mistakes, and the
chaotic structure of this page. And
if you're just looking for <b>The Anarchist Cookbook</b>, you won't
find it here. Bad luck...

<p><h3>Articles</h3>
<p><font size=4><b>I</b></font>f you want to contribute to our magazine, 
you can always E-mail us your articles and letters. We will translate 
them in dutch and if interesting we will publish it. 
<p><font size=4><b>T</b></font>he stuff that you send doesn't have to 
concern only anarchist topics, but of course we won't publish fascist, 
sexist, homophobic, etc. rubbish.
<p><h3>Lorenzo Komboa Ervin</h3>
<p><font size=4><b>W</b><font>e recently did an 
<a href="../nieuws/ervin.html">Interview</a> with 
<b>Lorenzo Komboa Ervin</b>, the author of 
<b>"Anarchism and the Black Revolution"</b>; Please check it out.
<p>
<h3>Solidarity to 504 arrested greek anarchists</h3>
<p>
<font size=4><b>T</b></font>here is a large financial problem  amongst 
anarchist groups in Greece. 
In particular, the collaboration of anarchist groups has a problem (ie 
anarhiki Paremvasi and Sispirosi). It maintains two offices, it has to 
pay lots of bills, rents. It owes lots of money due to the campaign on 
the 504 arrested anarchists during the Polytechnic riot. 9 of those 
arrested have been convicted to serve 40 months in jail and are in 
hiding. They have an account number: 157/882717-63, National Bank of 
Greece. The account is in the name of George Vlassopoulos. You can write 
to them at po box 30557, 10033 Athens Greece.
<p><font size=4><b>R</b></font>ead this and act!
<p><h3>Logo Archive</h3>
<p><font size=4><B>A</B></font> while ago we started scanning some of our
images, go and see our <a href="../logo/index.html.english">logo-archive</a>.
<p><h3>International Anarchist Meeting in Belgium</h3>
<p><font size=4><b>S</b></font>ome of us are involved in the organising of 
an Anarchist Summer Camp in the year 2000. The intention is to organise an 
International meeting of anarchists from all over the world. We are checking 
out for the moment if this plan is going to work out. We are currently 
looking for contacts all over the globe, checking out places, searching 
for accomodation,...
<p><font size=4><b>I</b></font>f you wish to contribute 
to this plan or wan't to share your ideas with us, please 
<a href="mailto:de_nar@knooppunt.be"><b>E-mail</b></a>. 
If you work for an anarchist 
organisation you can fill in the form and mail it to us,
so we can make contact.
