1990, 210 p., 250fr<br>
<dd> <img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"><b>Harper, Gould, Clover(eds.) : Visions of Poesy : An Anthology of 20th Century Anarchist Poesy. </b>
<dt>Freedom Press, 1994, 301
p., 450 fr
</dl>
<br>
<br>
<h3><a name="E">STRIPS & CARTOONS</a></h3>
<br>
<br>
<dl>
<dd><img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"> <b>Daniels : Breaking Free, The Adventures of Tintin. </b>
<dt>Attack
International, 1994, 175 p. 200 fr<br>
<dd><img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"> <b>Gnoe : Amen</b>
<dt>SL/SD, 66 p.(A4), 50 fr<br>
<dd><img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"><b>Roum Donald : Wildcat. </b>
<dt>Freedom Press, 1987, 48 p., 90 fr<br>
 <dd> <img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"><b>Wildcat strikes Again. </b>
<dt>1989, 48 p., 110 fr<br>
<dd><img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"><b>Wildcat ABC of bosses. </b>
<dt>1991, 48 p., 110 fr<br>
<dd><img align=bottom src="../ball.gif"><b>Health Service Wildcat</b>
<dt>1994, 48 p., 110 fr.<br>
</dl>
<br>
